          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>For complete light control, drapery remains the most<br/>effective window treatment. Crafted from richly textured fabrics and elegantly<br/>hungover windows, drapes provide exceptional privacy and superior light<br/>blockage.</p><p>The performance of drapery depends greatly on the fabric's color and construction.<br/>Generally, darker shades offer better light absorption, while denser, tightly<br/>woven fabrics provide greater opacity. The tighter the weave and the heavier<br/>the fabric, the more effective it becomes in blocking light and creating a<br/>comfortable, private space.</p>",
            "text_style": "body"
          }
        },
